{"id": "1336667383422521346", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "author_id": "512881362223759360", "author_name": "x013318908", "content": "黒印（ブラックシール）は調査中だけで使える通貨ですけど、これで強くなる覚醒体もいて意外。\nこの才能（天賦）は密契で強化できます？", "timestamp": "2025-02-05T11:58:58.287000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1336667383586357299", "filename": "DCC5FE3D-223E-467A-B427-1A60B5C0E8F8.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 123620, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1300659436804640788/1336667383586357299/DCC5FE3D-223E-467A-B427-1A60B5C0E8F8.jpg?ex=6a372942&is=6a35d7c2&hm=13d54a1f621f3f86316aebdef54d4edf207e56d11c714ba123e81dca60ebc22e&"}]}
